name: Fish-O-Fish: The Arcade Game
description:
Have you ever fed a fish to a fish ?

Now you can. Fish-O-Fish: The Arcade Game helps you to do so. Just do the following:-

1) Eat

2) Evolve

3) Create High Scores

It's not so difficult right ! Try it out. You'll get to know.

Only for ANDROID
